TAB Engineers required for Doha Qatar
-
Date Posted: 2014/05/05 18:00:08
Ref. JB3047561
Job Description
Progressive Engineering is representing a Top 15 MEP Contractor who have operations across the GCC and North Africa. With a successful track record in both Infrastructure and Civil operations our client is continuing to grow and develop from strength to strength.Due to the award of a number of recent projects they have partnered with Progressive Engineering to hire a number of TAB Engineers required for multiple projects in Doha Qatar.Candidates are required to have demonstable experience in Testing and Balancing. Ideally 3 - 6 years, however due to the scale of requirements Progressive would be interested to interview and discuss all avenues available.Please not that these positions are permanent hires and not project based.To apply please submit you up to date CV emphasising your Testing and Balancing experience, and a Progessive Engineering consultant will endeavour to contact you.
Skills
Testing and Balancing
